data.description: Welcome to this beautifully maintained, mid-century gem that seamlessly combines character and comfort. Nestled on a sprawling one acre lot in a convenient location, this 3-bedroom, 1.5 bathroom home offers over 1,600 square feet of comfortable living space. Situated on the outskirts of Waxahachie, this home combines the serenity of rural living with quick access to the heart of downtown. Enjoy charming shops, boutiques, delectable dining, and a vibrant community while still enjoying the feel of the country. Being close to Interstate 35 makes commuting into Dallas a breeze. A highlight of this property is the expansive backyard, which opens up to limitless possibilities. With an acre of land at your disposal, you can create your own oasis, whether it's a beautiful garden, recreational space, or even build the workshop you've always dreamed of. There is a storm cellar on the property and storage sheds will remain with the home. Seller offering $2000 towards closing cost or buy down!
